name: Fastnate
body:
Fastnate is a [JPA](http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javaee/tech/persistence-jsp-140049.html "Java Persistence API")
tool to generate SQL statements without having access to a database. Its main use case is to create test data for databases during development time.

We are currently working on version 1.0, so stay tuned...
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
